Graphic Designer and videographer with a demonstrated history of working in the creative industry. Skilled in graphic design, video production, art direction, filmmaking and visual arts. Holds a BA from the Gerrit Rietveld Academy, where he began his studies in Fine Art, subsequently graduated from the Graphic Design department in 2018. He lives and works between Amsterdam and Italy. His practice consists of both commission based work as well as working on self-initiated projects/ research and collaborations with others.
